import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import usePlayers from "../../hooks/skrallgaming/usePlayers"; import Navbar from "../../components/navigation/skrallgaming/Navbar"; import "../../assets/style/skrallgaming/playerlist.css" export default function Calculator(){ const { players } = usePlayers() const [ selectedPlayers , setSelectedPlayers ] = useState([undefined, undefined, undefined, undefined]) const [ winningPercentage , SetWinningPercentage ] = useState(undefined) const [ gameType , setGameType ] = useState("smash2") const FindPlayer = (id, playerName) => { const player = players.find(player => player.name === playerName) let newSelectedPlayers = [...selectedPlayers] newSelectedPlayers[id] = player setSelectedPlayers(newSelectedPlayers) } const playerOptions = () => { //Denna körs för mkt, kör i en useEffect på ngt sätt istället.. return( <> { players.map(player => ( )) } ) } useEffect(() => { if(selectedPlayers.includes(undefined)) return if (gameType === "beerPong") SetWinningPercentage(parseInt((1 / (1 + Math.pow(10, (selectedPlayers[2].beerPong + selectedPlayers[3].beerPong - (selectedPlayers[0].beerPong + selectedPlayers[1].beerPong)) / 400)))*100)) else SetWinningPercentage(parseInt((1 / (1 + Math.pow(10, (selectedPlayers[2].rating + selectedPlayers[3].rating - (selectedPlayers[0].rating + selectedPlayers[1].rating)) / 400)))*100)) }, selectedPlayers) return <>
